Follow These Commands step by step To install kali in Termux

apt update 
apt upgrade
pkg install wget
wget -O install-nethunter-turmux https://offs.ec/2MceZWr
chmod +x install-nethunter-turmux
./install-nethunter-termux

Then You can Delete Rootfs By typing N. 

And then You will be able to use kali. 

